**Topic check:** Vectors. The tag is correct.

**Solution**

\[
\overrightarrow{GF}=-\overrightarrow{FG}
=\begin{pmatrix}5\\-2\end{pmatrix}
\]

\[
\overrightarrow{HF}
=\overrightarrow{HG}+\overrightarrow{GF}
=\begin{pmatrix}4\\14\end{pmatrix}
+\begin{pmatrix}5\\-2\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}9\\12\end{pmatrix}
\]

Magnitude:

\[
|\overrightarrow{HF}|=\sqrt{9^2+12^2}=15
\]

**Answer:** \(15\).
